#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn47.30"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn47.30:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 47 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 47 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.30:0.2"
msgid "3. Sīlaṭṭhitivagga "
msgstr "3. Ethics and Duration "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn47.30:0.3"
msgid "30. Mānadinnasutta "
msgstr "30. With Mānadinna "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.178, sc1
msgctxt "sn47.30:1.1"
msgid "Taṃyeva nidānaṃ. "
msgstr "The same setting. "

msgctxt "sn47.30:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena mānadinno gahapati ābādhiko hoti dukkhito bāḷhagilāno. "
msgstr "Now at that time the householder Mānadinna was sick, suffering, gravely ill. "

msgctxt "sn47.30:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho mānadinno gahapati aññataraṃ purisaṃ āmantesi: "
msgstr "Then he addressed a man: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.30:1.4"
msgid "“ehi tvaṃ, ambho purisa … pe … "
msgstr "“Please, mister, go to Venerable Ānanda …” … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.30:1.5"
msgid "na me, bhante, khamanīyaṃ na yāpanīyaṃ. Bāḷhā me dukkhā vedanā abhikkamanti, no paṭikkamanti; abhikkamosānaṃ paññāyati, no paṭikkamoti. "
msgstr "“Sir, I’m not keeping well, I’m not alright. The pain is terrible and growing, not fading; its growing is evident, not its fading. "

msgctxt "sn47.30:1.6"
msgid "Evarūpāya cāhaṃ, bhante, dukkhāya vedanāya phuṭṭho samāno kāye kāyānupassī viharāmi ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ; "
msgstr "When I experience such painful feelings I meditate observing an aspect of the body—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world. "

msgctxt "sn47.30:1.7"
msgid "vedanāsu … pe … "
msgstr "I meditate observing an aspect of feelings … "

msgctxt "sn47.30:1.8"
msgid "citte … pe … "
msgstr "mind … "

msgctxt "sn47.30:1.9"
msgid "dhammesu dhammānupassī viharāmi ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. "
msgstr "principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world. "

msgctxt "sn47.30:1.10"
msgid "Yāni cimāni, bhante, bhagavatā pañcorambhāgiyāni saṃyojanāni desitāni, nāhaṃ, bhante, tesaṃ kiñci attani appahīnaṃ samanupassāmī”ti. "
msgstr "And of the five lower fetters taught by the Buddha, I don’t see any that I haven’t given up.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.30:1.11"
msgid "“Lābhā te, gahapati, suladdhaṃ te, gahapati. "
msgstr "“You’re fortunate, householder, so very fortunate! "

msgctxt "sn47.30:1.12"
msgid "Anāgāmiphalaṃ tayā, gahapati, byākatan”ti. "
msgstr "You have declared the fruit of non-return.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn47.30:1.13"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn47.30:1.14"
msgid "Sīlaṭṭhitivaggo tatiyo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn47.30:2.1"
msgid "Sīlaṃ ṭhiti parihānaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn47.30:2.2"
msgid "suddhaṃ brāhmaṇapadesaṃ; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn47.30:2.3"
msgid "Samattaṃ loko sirivaḍḍho, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn47.30:2.4"
msgid "mānadinnena te dasāti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
